You have defeated many of the Orcs and Uruks who reside in Dâr Mauzur, weakening Ugrukhôr's forces.

Dâr Mauzur is sparsely populated with many who served under Ugrukhôr before the fall of Sauron.
Defeat Orcs and Uruks at Dâr Mauzur
Orcs and Uruks can be found at Dâr Mauzur.\n\nYou should defeat as many Orcs and Uruks as possible.

The encampment stretches a great distance along the base of the Morgai. It is sparsely populated with many who served under Ugrukhôr before the fall of Sauron. These foes should be dealt with before Ugrukhôr is able to turn his attention to reclaiming his former forces.
